.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"f34d4ab9a6d9e9afade271ca9f82eca1f0fb760d","tid":2068381,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8a5777569076c2e526d5dd3c86524b2c1ba5b4","tid":2068381,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"希望樓主早日收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925427ea871bf4c88f2bb7d19a4329556d4515e7","tid":2068381,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f34d4ab9a6d9e9afade271ca9f82eca1f0fb760d","tid":2068381,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8a5777569076c2e526d5dd3c86524b2c1ba5b4","tid":2068381,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"希望樓主早日收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"你咁撚煩咁撚仆街，自己唔改，只係指意人地就晒你！<br />\n快撚啲收皮啦，條仔大把選擇，點解要受你啲仆街性格行為"},{"pid":"80c2012132af6dbb56d13d8b14042339a16e6435","tid":2068381,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"戇鳩少陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmo