own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c564cbef059091878fdb18c4bd871af49a21bc40","tid":2068381,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"好辛苦 想發洩下<br />\n唔想再情緒勒索人<br />\n好嘔心<br />\n有時真係希望男朋友可以飛撚咗我 搵過另一個好啲嘅女仔<br />\n等佢可以幸福 拍拖真係可以開開心心<br />\n唔撚洗次次都要見到個女朋友喊喊喊"},{"pid":"f61baf4a35066005f4e52efaa8a45d4daa732bf8","tid":2068381,"uid":192769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c564cbef059091878fdb18c4bd871af49a21bc40","tid":2068381,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"好辛苦 想發洩下<br />\n唔想再情緒勒索人<br />\n好嘔心<br />\n有時真係希望男朋友可以飛撚咗我 搵過另一個好啲嘅女仔<br />\n等佢可以幸福 拍拖真係可以開開心心<br />\n唔撚洗次次都要見到個女朋友喊喊喊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"發洩下lor<br />\n佢同得你一齊實有原因既，一定係你有d 野吸引佢。<br />\n愛情唔係要搵最好果個，而係要搵最岩你果個。<br />\n唔好期望佢搵過個會點好點好。最起碼佢依家鐘意果個係你阿ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 通常d 靚女都會話自己唔靚，好瘦又會話自己好肥。你又話自己唔靚又話自己肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714e0dd18a9ae27dd244c3aefdd632b1bd1255c4","tid":2068381,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f61baf4a35066005f4e52efaa8a45d4daa